{"tid":1045273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出席集會言論百無禁忌 特朗普陶醉攬國旗被批「有病」","createTime":"2019-03-03T13:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:39:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c61c61c494753b77b7132e39891549fc28313e7","tid":1045273,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190303/large/1551597970_242a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190303%2Flarge%2F1551597970_242a.jpg&h=bc918bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普周六到馬里蘭州出席保守政治行動會議（CPAC），揚言自己會在2020年成功連任，演講中肆意批評政敵，言論可謂百無禁忌。他出場時又大動作擁抱美國國旗，一臉陶醉，被批評舉止「噁心」、「有病」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普步進講台時，以誇張動作擁抱美國國旗，背景同時播着《天佑美國》（God Bless the USA），支持者大聲歡呼。特朗普在CPAC發表兩個多小時演說，揚言自己會以更大優勢勝出2020年的總統選舉、成功爭取連任。台下觀眾反應熱烈，高呼「美國、美國、美國」。<br />\n不過，有人批評特朗普擁抱國旗的舉動「噁心」、「古怪」、「令人尷尬」。有人寫道：「很古怪。我沒見過世界上很多領袖（古今）會這樣做。」有人直接批評他「這個人有病」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普演說時肆意嘲笑民主黨人應對氣候變化的環保政策，他道：「他們應努力推動&hellip;&hellip;沒有飛機、沒有能源。當沒有風吹時，你們就沒有電用了。大家快點吧，親愛的，今天有風吹過嗎？親愛的，我想看電視。」<br />\n特朗普批評「通俄門」特別檢察官米勒（Robert Muller）的調查是「狗屎」，暗示有移民背景的國會議員「仇恨我們國家」，又批評聯儲局主席鮑威爾（Jerome Powell）「喜歡調高利率」。評論指特朗普在這場演說中可謂「百無禁忌」，除了批評民主黨，亦談到墮胎、移民等議題，甚至還誓言要針對某些不捍衛保守言論的大學院校，要扣下他們的聯邦研究經費補助。<br />\n民主黨全國委員會發言人韋塞爾(Daniel Wessel)回應時，直斥特朗普的演說「怪異、神經錯亂的胡言亂語」。<br />\n英國《都市報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190303/59324347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59324347&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=32206d0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59324347&h=a14d3ea1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190303/59324347</a>"},{"pid":"f493a0e437f23b262f06aa96b6d4e919fdedffa7","tid":1045273,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad572883b5b6bc30757b38831f312cee1769eca","tid":1045273,"uid":58552,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"就係侵呼個吸 都屌佢排放過多二氧化碳"},{"pid":"74e6d2bb652e32d0956fa0c35862dc112306135b","tid":1045273,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"好撚可愛 想J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c30acf1a34c1f5dee0b2addbcd94cf51c26345","tid":1045273,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"愛國都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684296b6b5f79cbf8b26c02841b4ece3893afd51","tid":1045273,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"邊個咁樣講？"},{"pid":"8dac312d7cf9e5a197fa687e7a8191d569f1b7f3","tid":1045273,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"班左膠未見過肛澤民你外國出醜既新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413832082356f7807b810b21870ac56428e991d5","tid":1045273,"uid":74757,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/220949_e527e165cce46a8e63e344a164611826.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F220949_e527e165cce46a8e63e344a164611826.png&h=c7df8fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都唔係第一次發生,2016已經咁做"},{"pid":"c92d1109b4ee08f1ce0eb399fa5569e5a1f34b48","tid":1045273,"uid":13281,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"一個平時咁狠咁嚴肅既人會做啲咁白痴既野<br />\n一係佢真心愛呢個國